 Ticketmaster 数据泄露后，Live Nation 面临数百万美元的集体诉讼https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-nation-faceing-multi-million-dollar-class-action-lawsuit-after-huge-ticketmaster-data-breach-3802932?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=巨额票务大师数据泄露后，活生生的国家面临数百万美元的集体诉讼Liberty DunworthTue, 15 Oct 2024 14:14:17 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3802932 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Live Nation 徽标，背景中可见 Ticketmaster，" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>黑客获取了 5.6 亿客户的详细信息，并威胁以 50 万美元出售这些数据</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-nation-facing-multi-million-dollar-class-action-lawsuit-after-huge-ticketmaster-data-breach-3802932">由于 Ticketmaster 数据泄露，Live Nation 面临数百万美元的集体诉讼，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Live Nation 徽标，背景中可见 Ticketmaster，" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster-design@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，继今年早些时候 Ticketmaster 发生大规模数据泄露事件后，Live Nation 正面临价值数百万美元的集体诉讼。</p><p>据<a href="https://consequence.net/2024/10/live-nation-lawsuit-ticketmaster-data-breach/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Consequence 报道</em></a>，今年 4 月有报道称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-urges-users-to-carry-out-checks-as-560million-customers-data-stolen-and-held-ransom-by-hackers-3760885">一个名为 ShinyHunters 的黑客组织访问了 Ticketmaster 数据库并窃取了 1.3 TB 数据</a>，此后提起诉讼。</p><p>这两家公司于 2010 年合并，今年早些时候遭到黑客攻击后，据称从两家公司获得了详细信息，包括全名、地址、电子邮件地址、电话号码、门票销售和活动详细信息、订单信息以及部分支付卡数据。 5.6 亿客户。 ShinyHunters 随后威胁要以 500,000 美元（393,800 英镑）的价格出售这些数据。</p><p>最初，Ticketmaster <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-urges-users-to-carry-out-checks-as-560million-customers-data-stolen-and-held-ransom-by-hackers-3760885">敦促其用户因数据泄露而进行检查</a>，然后在 5 月份通过<a href="https://www.sec.gov/ix?doc=/Archives/edgar/data/0001335258/000133525824000081/lyv-20240520.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SEC 备案</a>确认了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-acknowledge-hackers-stealing-560million-customers-data-for-ransom-3762096">此事</a>。根据该文件，该公司于 5 月 20 日发现“包含公司数据的第三方云数据库环境”上存在未经授权的活动，并着手展开调查。</p><p>现在，包括<em>Consequence</em>在内的媒体已经报道了拟议的集体诉讼，并指控 Ticketmaster 和 Live Nation 在违规之前的疏忽行为。据报道，Ticketmaster 声称未能保护其客户的数据，也未能采取安全措施来防止攻击。 </p><figure id="attachment_3802937" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3802937" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3802937" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Ticketmaster 徽标显示在智能手机上，背景为 Live Nation 徽标。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Live-Nation-Ticketmaster@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3802937" class="wp-caption-text"> Ticketmaster 徽标显示在智能手机上，背景为 Live Nation 徽标。图片来源：Avishek Das/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>它还声称，Ticketmaster 没有及时通知客户他们的数据已被泄露。</p><p>根据该文件，据称数百万用户面临身份盗窃和垃圾邮件的风险增加，而 ShinyHunters 的黑客攻击是数据保护程序不足的结果。它正在寻求高达 500 万美元（380 万英镑）的赔偿，但具体金额不详。</p><p>这是一个正在发展的故事， <em>NME</em>已联系 Ticketmaster 和 Live Nation 征求意见。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/live-nation-lawsuit-ticketmaster-data-breach-1236031775/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>报道，ShinyHunters 在针对必胜客、AT&amp;T、GitHub 等公司的黑客攻击中窃取了 9 亿条消费者记录。</p><p>就在有关数据泄露的报道发布几天前，联合司法部对 Live Nation 提起了大规模的反垄断诉讼，并声称这家票务巨头采取了滥用措施来消除美国的竞争。</p><p>此后，Ticketmaster 因其在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">2025 年重聚巡演</a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/consumer-champion-which-ticketmaster-refund-fans-oasis-reunion-tickets-3792128">使用动态定价而受到批评</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">2025 年体育场巡演</a>的门票于 8 月开始销售，许多球迷 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">在购买门票时发现门票已经售罄，</a>感到沮丧。这是因为价格上涨意味着门票价格可能会根据需求在没有警告的情况下上涨或下跌。 </p><figure id="attachment_3457265" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3457265" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3457265" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo.jpg" alt="在这张照片插图中，智能手机上显示了 Ticketmaster 徽标。图片来源：Mateusz Slodkowski/GETTY" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/ticketmaster-logo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3457265" class="wp-caption-text">智能手机上显示的 Ticketmaster 徽标。图片来源：Mateusz Slodkowski/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p>一些排了一整天队的球迷在确认购买时支付了 355 英镑购买了原价 135 英镑的门票。 Ticketmaster 此前曾在其网站上澄清，门票“可能会根据需求随时增加或减少。这类似于机票和酒店房间的销售方式。”</p><p>这场争议导致文化部长丽莎·南迪（Lisa Nandy） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">呼吁对动态定价和二次门票销售进行审查</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keir-starmer-responds-to-oasis-price-hikes-calling-them-depressing-3790633">总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）则称价格上涨“令人沮丧”</a> 。此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-european-commission-reportedly-investigating-dynamic-pricing-amid-oasis-tickets-controversy-3790240">欧盟委员会目前也正在调查这一问题。</a></p><p>同样，在强烈反对之后，消费者品牌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/consumer-champion-which-ticketmaster-refund-fans-oasis-reunion-tickets-3792128">“Which”？呼吁Ticketmaster“做正确的事情，向那些可能被误导而支付巨额费用购买几小时前半价门票的粉丝退还差价”</a> 。</p><p> Ticketmaster 的一位代表在接受 Which? 采访时评论道：“我们致力于与竞争与市场管理局 (CMA) 合作，并期待与他们分享更多有关门票销售的事实。”</p><p>当<em>NME</em>寻求进一步评论时，Ticketmaster 发言人表示：“粉丝可以通过 Ticketmaster 或 Twickets 以全价转售他们的 Oasis 门票。”该发言人还分享了进一步的信息，即通过 Ticketmaster 购买的门票可在购买后 24 小时内通过其粉丝保证计划全额退款。 24小时后，门票将不再退款，只能出售。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/live-nation-facing-multi-million-dollar-class-action-lawsuit-after-huge-ticketmaster-data-breach-3802932">由于 Ticketmaster 数据泄露，Live Nation 面临数百万美元的集体诉讼，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
